{"title":"linux下切换系统默认python版本","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.013Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux下切换系统默认python版本","updated":"2023-07-28T09:13:17.174Z","content":"<p><code>python -V</code>查看python版本<br>\n我系统默认的是python2<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0a38c9319ffb4949a16567a3243d8537.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>查看系统内的python路径</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">ls</span> /usr/bin/python*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0f8657ba293745689e3901188c550dae.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n下面切换版本<br>\n切换成python3</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">rm</span> -rf /usr/bin/python</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">ln</span> -s /usr/bin/python3  /usr/bin/python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>切换成python2</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">rm</span> -rf /usr/bin/python</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo <span class=\"built_in\">ln</span> -s /usr/bin/ptyhon2 /usr/bin/python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>第一句是删除系统对原有默认python的软连接<br>\n第二句是指定新的软链，需要用3就指定到3，用2就指定到2，即插即用。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境","link":"2023/07/28/Linux下从零配置Hadoop环境"},"next":{"title":"linux下配置gradle环境","link":"2023/07/28/linux下配置gradle环境"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/linux下切换系统默认python版本/","reading_time":"157 字约 1 分钟"}